          { "feature": "palpable_mass_or_abscess", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "IV antibiotics (e.g., Piperacillin-Tazobactam). CT-guided drainage of abscess if >4cm. Emergency laparotomy if generalized peritonitis. Hartmann procedure or primary resection with anastomosis."
